               </choice>
               <lb n="4"/>fecit; vixit
                <lb n="5"/>
               <expan><abbr>ann</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan>
               <num type="cardinal" value="50">L</num>, <expan><abbr>men</abbr><ex>sibus</ex></expan>
               <lb n="6"/>
               <num type="cardinal" value="10">X</num>.

            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>Aninia Hilara made (this) for her incomparable mother Claudia Arria; she lived for 50 years and 10 months.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>The hairstyle became fashionable by Julia Domna, the wife of the emperor Septimius
                    Severus (193-211). </p>
         </div>
